    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "BOISE, Jan 14.-State Auditor\nBragaw filed in the supreme court\ntoday a petition for a writ of pro-\nhibition to prevent Governor Good\ning and other state officials from\ninterfering with his administra-\nton of office. The contest origi-\nmates over Bragaw's refusal to is\nsue deficiency warrants in the\nMeyer, Haywood and Pettibone\ncases and the ensuing refusal of\nthe board of examiners to endorse\nsalary warrants OF Bragaw's wife\nand son, who are employed in his\noffice.\n\n\nBragaw has a $4,000 libel suit\npending against Gooding and the\nBoise statesmen."
    }
  ]
